Chrome exstension to quickly change case of any sentence

To load an chrome extension from local source, check this: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5W9ZPEaVMWE

Alternatively you can read the offical documentation here https://developer.chrome.com/docs/extensions/mv2/tut_debugging/

USING THE EXTENSION:

The extension has a simple UI

1. Paste the text in the text area.
2. Click the required case button
3. Case chnaged text is automatically copied to the clipboard

